<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Love Letter</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.16/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@1.3.0/dist/full.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Indie+Flower&display=swap');
    body {
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/flat-lay-photo-office-desk-with-laptop-copy-space-background_1150-45598.jpg?w=1480&t=st=1680121115~exp=1680121715~hmac=788adddfa8276fbb7654a74987db8e211b5bb8ffc1a7eccd4494f5749b0bb928');
      background-size: cover;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      font-family: 'Indie Flower', cursive;
    }
    .paper-note {
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/white-texture_1160-786.jpg?w=1480&t=st=1680121212~exp=1680121812~hmac=406fef25f6a53d591782106d453c1c3e7000860a4875bd48d2f24325a4794f03');
      background-size: cover;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
    <div class="paper-note rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <img src="/assets/tomiami.png" alt="Paper Heart 3" class="w-96 h-96 flex sm:hidden">
      <h1 class="text-4xl mb-6 text-center px-4">Dania's Love Letter to Miami</h1>
    <article class="px-5">
    <p class="text-xl mb-4">
        My dearest Miami,
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4">
        From the moment I first saw you, I knew you were the one. Your smile lights up my world, and your laughter fills my heart with joy.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4">
        The times we've spent together have been some of the happiest moments of my life. I cherish every second we spend in each other's company, and I look forward to creating even more memories together in the future.
  </p>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    Our love is like a beautiful symphony, with each note complementing the other, creating a harmonious melody that resonates deep within my soul. You are my inspiration, my muse, and my greatest love.
  </p>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    I promise to always be by your side, to support and encourage you in everything you do. Together, we can overcome any obstacle and achieve our dreams. With you, I am whole, and I am complete.
  </p>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    Thank you for being the love of my life and for filling my heart with immeasurable happiness. I can't wait to see what our future holds, and I am so grateful for every moment we share.
  </p>
  <p class="text-xl mb-4">
    Forever yours,
  </p>
  <p class="text-xl">
    [Your Name]
  </p>
  </article>
</div>
 </div>
  <!-- Add paper hearts and stencils on the desk -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full items-start justify-start p-6 hidden sm:flex">
<img src="paper-heart-1.png" alt="Paper Heart 1" class="w-24 h-24 mt-12 ml-12 opacity-70">
<img src="paper-heart-2.png" alt="Paper Heart 2" class="w-20 h-20 mt-32 ml-32 opacity-70">
<img src="/assets/tomiami.png" alt="Paper Heart 3" class="w-60 h-60 mt-48 ml-20">

  </div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-full h-full hidden sm:flex items-end justify-end p-6">
    <img src="stencil-1.png" alt="Stencil 1" class="w-32 h-32 mb-12 mr-16 opacity-70">
    <img src="stencil-2.png" alt="Stencil 2" class="w-24 h-24 mb-24 mr-24 opacity-70">
    <img src="stencil-3.png" alt="Stencil 3" class="w-16 h-16 mb-32 mr-12 opacity-70">
  </div>
</body>
</html>